oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Pat O'Daniel & His Hillbilly Boys - #204
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Pat O'Daniel & His Hillbilly Boys radio program #204. Featuring Pat O'Daniel, Mickey Wickey (Mike O'Daniel), Leon the Texas Songbird (Leon Huff), and Horace the Love Bird (Kermit Whalin). Sponsored by W. Lee O'Daniel Flour Co.'s Hillbilly Flour brand.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Pat O'Daniel; Hillbilly Boys
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Announcer opening statement -- Theme (I Like Mountain Music) -- Opening statement (Pat O'Daniel) -- Tumbling Tumbleweeds (Leon Huff, Kermit Whalin) -- Hillbilly Flour commercial (Pat O'Daniel) -- Pat O'Daniel introduces 'Horace' -- The Dying Rustler (Kermit Whalin) -- Pat O'Daniel introduces 'Mickey Wickey' and Leon Huff -- Going Up Caney (Mike O'Daniel fiddle, Leon Huff calls) -- Pat O'Daniel introduces 'Mickey Wickey' -- Mike O'Daniel reads poem Give A Helping Hand -- Pat O'Daniel introduces Leon Huff -- Crawdad Song (Leon Huff) -- Closing statement (Pat O'Daniel) -- Theme (I Like Mountain Music) -- Announcer closing statement
